              <p style={{ fontFamily: sans, fontSize: 13, lineHeight: 1.9, color:"#FBF7EE", fontWeight: 300, marginBottom: 24 }}>The Master track is the academic and professional foundation of Excalibur. Students study public speaking, financial literacy, business strategy, sales and marketing, investing, AI, leadership, negotiation, and human psychology — taught by founders, top CEOs, Wall Street executives, investors, and industry leaders.</p>
