              <p style={{ fontFamily: sans, fontSize: 13, lineHeight: 1.9, color:"#FBF7EE", fontWeight: 300 }}>This is the track that shapes how students lead, speak, influence, and engage with the world. Running continuously throughout the entire ten-month experience.</p>
