                <h2 style={{ fontFamily: serif, fontSize: "clamp(28px,3vw,42px)", fontWeight: 600, color:"#d8b78c", lineHeight: 1.0, marginBottom: 8 }}>Excalibur "Ivy" Portfolio</h2>
