                  <p style={{ fontFamily:sans, fontSize:13, color:"#FBF7EE", fontWeight:300, lineHeight:1.9, marginBottom:28 }}>Faculty guide each team through structured milestones. Selected ventures may receive seed support from the Excalibur network of investors and mentors.</p>
