                  <p style={{ fontFamily:sans, fontSize:13, color:"#010000", fontWeight:300, lineHeight:1.9, marginBottom:14 }}>Students build an initiative, program, or organization designed to address a real problem in their community or beyond. They apply the same business disciplines as the commercial track — research, positioning, outreach, partnerships, and financial modeling — while measuring success through impact alongside revenue.</p>
