                      <p style={{ fontFamily:sans, fontSize:14, lineHeight:1.9, color:"#FBF7EE", fontWeight:300, marginBottom:16 }}>Every session includes live studio time. Students build their chosen venture — Da Vinci (commercial) or Medici (community impact) — with direct faculty coaching in the room. Every session produces a deliverable. Faculty hold every team to a professional benchmark.</p>
