              <h2 style={{ fontFamily:serif, fontSize:isMobile?52:80, fontWeight:300, color:"#d8b78c", lineHeight:0.95, letterSpacing:"-0.035em", margin:0 }}>Public Speaking<br/><em style={{ color:"#d8b78c" }}>&amp; Executive Rhetoric.</em></h2>
