              <h2 style={{ fontFamily:serif, fontSize:isMobile?"clamp(36px,8vw,52px)":"clamp(44px,4.5vw,68px)", fontWeight:300, color:"#010000", lineHeight:0.95, letterSpacing:"-0.03em", margin:0 }}>Foundation Semester<br/><em style={{ fontStyle:"italic" }}>Curriculum.</em></h2>
