            <div>
              <p style={{ fontFamily:eyebrow_font, fontSize:8, letterSpacing:"0.5em", color:"#d8b78c", fontWeight:600, textTransform:"uppercase", marginBottom:20 }}>Foundation Term · Every Session · Final Block</p>
              <h2 style={{ fontFamily:serif, fontSize:isMobile?40:64, fontWeight:300, color:"#FBF7EE", lineHeight:0.95, letterSpacing:"-0.03em", margin:0 }}>The<br/><em style={{ color:"#d8b78c" }}>War Room.</em></h2>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p style={{ fontFamily:sans, fontSize:14, lineHeight:1.9, color:"#FBF7EE", fontWeight:300 }}>Every session ends with a live business simulation. No preparation. No right answers guaranteed. Students think, argue, decide, and defend their judgment under faculty pressure. Fourteen weeks of War Room across the Foundation Term — five rotating formats, each designed to test a different dimension of business judgment and character.</p>
