            <p style={{ fontFamily:sans, fontSize:12, color:"#FBF7EE", fontWeight:300, lineHeight:1.8 }}>✦ Erik Dostal (Dean of Admissions) leads selected modules across both semesters. Guest practitioners rotate monthly for Industry Sectors. Outside specialists join for Legal Foundations, Personal Finance, and Public Relations. <button onClick={()=>setPage&&setPage("faculty")} style={{ fontFamily:eyebrow_font, background:"none", border:"none", color:"#d8b78c", fontSize:10, letterSpacing:"0.15em", cursor:"pointer", textDecoration:"underline", padding:0 }}>Meet the full faculty →</button></p>
