            <p style={{ fontFamily:sans, fontSize:14, lineHeight:1.9, color:"#FBF7EE", fontWeight:300, margin:0 }}>Beyond the weekly sessions, the Foundation Term includes a structured calendar of events, competitions, professional experiences, and milestone moments. Some are part of tuition. Some are optional and priced separately. All of them are intentional.</p>
