                <p style={{ fontFamily:sans, fontSize:14, color:"#FBF7EE", fontWeight:300, lineHeight:1.95, marginBottom:20 }}>Students applying for the Full Academic Year submit one application for both semesters. Accepted students receive Foundation Semester placement and automatic continuation into the Venture Semester, provided they remain in good standing.</p>
