            <p style={{ fontFamily:sans, fontSize:13, color:"#FBF7EE", fontWeight:300, lineHeight:1.85, opacity:.7, margin:0 }}>Students spend sixteen weeks building real ventures through seven venture disciplines, a live Venture Studio, and hands-on execution under the guidance of founders, investors, and industry leaders. Click any section below to explore.</p>
