          <h2 style={{ fontFamily:serif, fontSize:isMobile?"clamp(36px,8vw,60px)":"clamp(52px,6vw,88px)", fontWeight:300, color:"#FBF7EE", lineHeight:1, letterSpacing:"-0.04em", textAlign:"center", margin:0 }}>What this semester<br/><em style={{ color:"#d8b78c" }}>prepares your student for.</em></h2>
